<path d="M15.2 12.2 C15.4 13.4 15.8 13.8 17 14 C15.8 14.2 15.4 14.6 15.2 15.8 C15 14.6 14.6 14.2 13.4 14 C14.6 13.8 15 13.4 15.2 12.2 Z" />`,
